30 CITIZEN CENTERS. The appropriation in this act for Senior Citizen Centers
31 shall be distributed in the same manner as the funding formula requirements
32 set out in the federal Older Americans Act funding law. The additional
33 funding provided by this provision shall supplement and not supplant any
34 monies currently funding services for Senior Citizen Centers.
35 The requirements in this section shall only be implemented in accordance
36 with any necessary approval by the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services
